- **Propagate (P) and Generate (G) signals**: P = a ^ b (carry passes through), G = a & b (carry generated).
- **Fixed-depth carry computation**: Uses only OR/AND operations, achieving O(1) depth.
- **Correct 128-bit carry propagation**: Ensure carries propagate correctly across all four lanes.

