- `popcount128(0xFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFULL, 0xFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFULL)` returns 128 (all bits set)

The SWAR algorithm processes all 64 bits in parallel using bitmasks to accumulate counts efficiently.

